<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵，<delay20 />昨天我太緊張了，<delay8 />
所以都沒什麼睡呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />為了避免打瞌睡，<delay20 />
捕蟲的時候得小心才行呢～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />捕蟲大會馬上就要開始了呢，<delay20 />
我正在附近散步，<delay20 />
讓心情放鬆一點喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />捕蟲界的盛典，<delay20 />
「捕蟲大會」<delay20 />就要開始了<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay8 />
你準備好了嗎？<10_4 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />捕蟲大會是9點開始喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我在捕蟲大會當中<delay20 />
的基本方針就是<delay20 />
Catch and release！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />以捕蟲運動為前提之下，<delay20 />
和昆蟲的交涉以及<delay20 /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />捕蟲行為<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你沒在聽吧～！</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗨，<delay8 />你發現昆蟲了嗎？<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />和我的感覺<delay8 />Match的昆蟲，<delay20 />
怎麼還沒出現呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是我要求的標準<delay20 />
太高了嗎<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我沒想到今天居然會捕得這麼順利～<10_4 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這也都多虧了<delay20 />
<tag a="110" b="10" />的粉絲們支持呢！
<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對了，<delay20 />
接下來的Hero interview<delay20 />
是在哪裡進行呢？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果要問我的話，<delay20 />
比起追著什麼跑，我覺得自己還是<delay8 />
比較適合被追呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你今天參加大會的狀況如何？<delay20 />
<tag a="110" b="4" />？<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我覺得自己<delay20 />
捕得還算不錯喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所謂的捕蟲啊，<delay20 />
就是一場你來我往的<delay20 />
拉鋸戰呢！
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />現在<tag a="110" b="0" />就某方面來說，<delay20 />
是處在拉的階段呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
我能理解你想找我聊天的心情，<delay20 />
不過這樣你就沒空參加大會了吧？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="012" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看到第一眼的瞬間，<delay20 />
就有種電流通過全身的感覺<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我剛剛<delay8 />體驗到這種狀況了。
<anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊，<delay8 />我是在說昆蟲啦。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然最後還是被牠給逃了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="013" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在捕蟲的時候，<delay20 />
我覺得<delay8 />應該跟昆蟲保持一種<delay20 />
「剛剛好的距離」呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果靠得太近，<delay20 />
牠們會害羞得逃走喔～</message>
</msbt>